  "term": "def:pointwise-scalar-multiple-of-a-function",
  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Pointwise Scalar Multiple of a Function",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $X\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$, let $f:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$, and let\n$c\\in\\mathbb{R}$. The pointwise scalar multiple $cf:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$ is\nthe function defined by\n\\[\n (cf)(x)=c f(x)\n \\qquad (x\\in X).\n\\]",
